c0d","tid":1750213,"uid":206167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ca30602df5da3bc06a01083cf1609c6594eb41a","tid":1750213,"uid":21137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:26:29.000Z","msg":"咁應該大家都俾tg搞到瘋狂爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底點搞好，a酸真係有用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T13:04:32.000Z","msg":"我狀況同一樣，但塊面仲差啲，10月1之前已經間中食tg，搞到塊面勁差<br />\n10月1嗰日返到屋企啲瘡發到勁大同又多左，兩邊面70%都係瘡，洗完面仲會流到成面血，之後生左2舊囊種型嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似咁，不過我嗰舊仲大舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後頂唔順10月中到睇醫生開始食a酸，而家就嚟2個月，好係好左，不過就成塊面都係好深色嘅印<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">食a酸之前係咁唧</span>都唔知最後會唔會好返哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過我暫時覺得a酸係有啲效，希望你都快啲好"},{"pid":"dbfef6818b5088bb2661e5adbc414abb86e0dc6e","tid":1750213,"uid":37954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T13:05:56.000Z","msg":"屌我都係<br />\n生完左面生右面<br />\n係咁loop"},{"pid":"07802a65de6d4d1f4a01b03b07c63a701ff05f11","tid":1750213,"uid":86659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9762d2e6d006a09ec77244a05e876a4e3d10a9f2","tid":1750213,"uid":189214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d4ec552275ced264a98e5bbc11cf2ebaef77433","tid":1750213,"uid":38745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10e286027fb98707a8eb3f97a2be40db4952e3bc","tid":1750213,"uid":189214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"你啲暗瘡特徵同我一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />塊面就黎爛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:28:54.000Z","msg":"可能點算啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c